The paper deals with improving image recognition models using adversarial examples, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method also involves the use of auxiliary batch normalization, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the threat of adversarial examples, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
